---
import "../../styles/tokens.css";
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Docs — Shane Turon</title>
</head>
<body class="gallery-body">
  <div class="gallery-wrap expansion-landing">
    <p class="expansion-host">docs.shaneturon.ca</p>
    <h1>Documentation</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Execution specs, routing orders, and wrapper references.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>ORDER-001 routing — <code>docs/ORDER-001-ROUTING.md</code> in repo</li>
      <li>ORDER-025 expansion subdomains — <code>docs/ORDER-025-EXPANSION-SUBDOMAINS.md</code></li>
      <li><a href="/projects/">Gallery case files</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

<style>
  .expansion-landing { max-width: 40rem; }
  .expansion-host {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .expansion-landing ul { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; }
  .expansion-landing a { color: var(--accent); }
  code { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #cbd5e1; }
</style>
